INITIAL BUILD:

1. After cloning the repository in the ideal location, type the command: make
2. If dependencies are missing, the build will "fail" due to lack of permission; in this case, type the command: sudo make
3. Enter the directory, "BUBBLES", by typing the command: cd CIR/BUBBLES
4. Once inside the directory, "BUBBLES", type the command: make (NOTE two bubbles will be constructed inside of a directory called "bubs"


INITAL BUILD FAILURE:

1. In the event of a build failure, it is important to kill any background processes involved in the build that were unable to close correctly. To do this, simply
	type the command: kill -9 -1
2. in the directory CIR/BUBBLES, type the command: make
